<section id="about">
  <p class="about-title">{title}</p>
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-text animate-fade-in">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Yixuan. Born in China 🇨🇳, I've lived and studied in the UK 🇬🇧
        and Germany 🇩🇪, and now I'm based in Zurich, Switzerland 🇨🇭. I'm
        passionate about technology—from Natural Language Processing to web
        development and 3D modeling. I've taught myself tools like Blender,
        Astro, and Three.js, and I'm always excited to learn more. <br /><br />

        When I'm not coding, I love traveling 🛥️, cycling 🚴🏻‍♀️, playing badminton
        🏸, and catching Pokémons :P I enjoy meeting new people, exploring new
        places, and taking on challenges that push me to grow. For me, life's
        all about turning “I can't” into “I did.” ✨ <br /><br />

        Let's connect and create something amazing together!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image animate-fade-in">
      <img src="/me.jpg" alt="About Me Image" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
